data.text:
When Stephen Hensley was born on 12 May 1909, in Liggett, Harlan, Kentucky, United States, his father, Gilbert Hensley, was 52 and his mother, Massie Daniel, was 28. He married Pearl Hibbard on 16 September 1930, in Wallins Creek, Harlan, Kentucky, United States. They were the parents of at least 1 daughter. He lived in United States in 1949 and Harlan, Harlan, Kentucky, United States in 1950. He died on 11 July 1988, in Harlan, Kentucky, United States, at the age of 79.
